    "description": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877720/extras/87d1f5cd04bb1bf890dc01fea8204faa.avif?t=1749668269\" width=600 height=100 /></span>There's trouble brewing on the horizon..... the Trojan Reef prepares for imminent invasion.... and you're dealing with lazy vampires, uppity skeletons, drunk sea monsters, and, perhaps worst of all, <i>teenagers in love</i>. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Perry is in charge of Barn Owl Company, perhaps the worst outfit to ever grace the Trojan Reef. Somehow, you and your team will outwit and outgun the humans as you race to save the last of the Rainbow Unicorns. </p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877720/extras/eb6ec3c432d884a3bf7380c6399071be.avif?t=1749668269\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >In no way related to the other Army of Tentacles games where the characters have the same exact names. What would make you think that?</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><img class=\"bb_img\" src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/1877720/extras/9029f10d6b88ca70584edab9b3e0f15a.avif?t=1749668269\" width=600 height=100 /></span></p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Party-based story and combat!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >  </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > <strong>A SILENT PROTAGONIST</strong>: Almost a fully voiced cast! Kind of! Just like the first game that started this all, Perry is completely silent! This is totally for artistic and tropey purposes and not at all due to budgeting! Gordon Freeman was silent, right? </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Whale Jesus (and MORE!) </p></li></ul><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Choices throughout the game may lead to unintended consequences Just like Gordon Freeman, right?</p></li></ul>",
